(Only for directors)

174
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,400
It's okay. Take it slow.

175
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,359
You'll get a chance to get in there.

176
00:13:26,599 --> 00:13:27,599
I'll re-check the contract out

177
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:28,719
