178
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,520
Maybe I can find more clues from it.

179
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:33,119
Thank you, Qin Yao.

180
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:34,440
You're welcome.

181
00:13:34,599 --> 00:13:35,599
I'm glad that I can help you.

182
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,440
